com.nokia.mid.voip
Interface VoipSettingsStateListener

public interface VoipSettingsStateListener

Interface for receiving asynchronous updates for state changes related to application's settings. Application should implement this interface and register its implementation with the setVoipSettingsStateListener method in VoipSettings.

States are defined in VoipStates class. Causes are defined in VoipCauses class.

See Also:
VoipSettings
